---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | Yee Hauls';
const description = 'How Yee Hauls LLC collects and uses information submitted through this website.';
const effective = 'June 23, 2026';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} path="/privacy/">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px;">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--muted);">This is a starting template. For final legal review, consult a licensed attorney in {site.stateFull}.</p>
      <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> {effective}</p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit our quote or contact form, we collect the information you provide, such as your name, phone number, email address, city, and a description of your job. We may also collect basic, non-identifying analytics about how visitors use this site.</p>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>We use your information to respond to your inquiry, provide a quote, schedule service, and improve our website.</p>

      <h2>SMS and text messaging</h2>
      <p>If you check the consent box and provide your phone number, you agree to receive text messages from {site.legalName} related to your quote and service, such as scheduling, confirmations, and updates. Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply. Reply STOP at any time to opt out, or HELP for help. Consent to receive text messages is not a condition of any purchase.</p>
      <p><strong>Mobile information and text messaging opt-in consent will never be shared with or sold to third parties or lead generators for any purpose.</strong></p>

      <h2>Who we share it with</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your information. We only share it with service providers that help us operate, such as our form delivery and analytics tools, and only as needed to run the business. As stated above, mobile information and SMS opt-in data are never shared with or sold to third parties or lead generators.</p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>You can request that we delete the information you submitted by emailing <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>{site.legalName}<br /><a href={`tel:${site.phoneE164}`}>{site.phoneDisplay}</a><br /><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
